HANBI: Hey! Wait!

223
00:07:53,933 --> 00:07:56,800
HANBI: So they are screaming.
They're not just screaming for no reason.

224
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:59,328
(For some reason, don't want to open the two doors)
- HANBI: Hey, I'm opening this. - JUSTIN: Open it.

225
00:07:59,488 --> 00:08:02,080
