227
00:08:03,136 --> 00:08:03,936
(Open)

228
00:08:04,288 --> 00:08:05,568
- HANBI: Ah!
- JUSTIN: Ah!

229
00:08:05,728 --> 00:08:06,976
(Empty)

230
00:08:07,099 --> 00:08:08,899
(Unexpected calmness)

231
00:08:09,233 --> 00:08:12,233
