- NICHOLAS: And the hair.

237
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,224
SONGHA: Was there hair?

238
00:08:24,333 --> 00:08:25,299
DANIEL: There was hair.

239
00:08:25,472 --> 00:08:29,600
