I didn't see it. - DANIEL: We ran at full speed.

240
00:08:29,849 --> 00:08:31,577
JUSTIN: Is it coming? Or not?

241
00:08:31,904 --> 00:08:35,593
(Arguing over the window) - HANBI: Ah! Wait.
Why is it open? - JUSTIN: Be sure. Make sure.

242
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,199
(Hair that ultimately couldn't fly in)

243
00:08:38,499 --> 00:08:40,566
HANBI: Just go...

244
00:08:41,888 --> 00:08:43,360
JUSTIN: Why did you make the color like this?

245
00:08:44,608 --> 00:08:45,632
JUSTIN: Seriously...

246
00:08:46,112 --> 00:08:47,633
JUSTIN: Why is it blue again?

247
00:08:48,064 --> 00:08:49,120
JUSTIN: Earlier, I...

