- JUSTIN: Hey, wait a minute.

303
00:10:34,336 --> 00:10:35,424
(Hi, I'm MINYEONG)

304
00:10:35,424 --> 00:10:36,544
TRAINEE: Hey, it might move.

305
00:10:36,933 --> 00:10:38,304
TRAINEE: Oh, it seems
this guy is about to charge forward.

306
00:10:38,766 --> 00:10:39,666
(Ah)

307
00:10:39,933 --> 00:10:40,866
(Charging is my thing)

308
00:10:41,866 --> 00:10:43,233
(Unlike the HANBI, who hid quickly)

309
00:10:43,766 --> 00:10:45,566
(JUSTIN ran away with full power)

310
00:10:46,433 --> 00:10:48,066
(DAEWON hasn't been able to stop since)

311
00:10:52,923 --> 00:10:53,664
(Gone)

312
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:57,200
(Polite ghost greeting and leaving)

313
00:10:57,566 --> 00:11:00,466
(DAEWON taking refuge behind the wall)

314
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:02,766
