HANBI: Where did you go? JUSTIN?

319
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,433
HANBI: How could you leave me behind?

320
00:11:16,466 --> 00:11:19,333
(Too serious to complain about his condition)

321
00:11:20,966 --> 00:11:21,766
JUSTIN: Just now...

322
00:11:22,566 --> 00:11:23,968
JUSTIN: I think I got around 6 seconds for 50m.

323
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,880
